==English==
===Proper noun===
'''Hanuman'''
#a [[Hindu]] [[demi-god]] who was a devotee of [[Rama]].  He was born to [[Anjana]] and [[Vayu].  He also plays a role of a god's servant in [[Mahabharata]].  He is also known as the ''monkey god''.
